>\n但呢一刻未到"},{"pid":"681c2bdb76c73f01fd01e1cca5432877e033fa26","tid":1205704,"uid":231206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:45:49.000Z","msg":"就算無人衝 班廢中廢老嘅立場都係唔會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不要千真以為 班廢中廢老會突然改變佢地對呢件事及集會人士嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係連不支持 不反對都不可能 佢地已經有既定嘅觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算只係靜坐 佢地都會一樣繼續話你收錢黎坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f776be4c8ce1cfb84712bfc4d7f70bc2705e9fc","tid":1205704,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:47:02.000Z","msg":"過二讀即衝"},{"pid":"8832ce9a829d0ec61348a092fdc80cb109c16d10","tid":1205704,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"681c2bdb76c73f01fd01e1cca5432877e033fa26","tid":1205704,"uid":231206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:45:49.000Z","msg":"就算無人衝 班廢中廢老嘅立場都係唔會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不要千真以為 班廢中廢老會突然改變佢地對呢件事及集會人士嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係連不支持 不反對都不可能 佢地已經有既定嘅觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算只係靜坐 佢地都會一樣繼續話你收錢黎坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:47:27.000Z","msg":"呢個好同意，永遠改變唔到呢班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆老母就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1790b4e3d46f2795d0e90cda29441c083650d758","tid":1205704,"uid":66032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:10:02.000Z","msg":"你個朋友好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850494ef706df0f0679a9252bfe5b6f94953b0e6","tid":1205704,"uid":66032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc